= Friedrich Stampfer

Friedrich Stampfer is the long-time editor-in-chief of Vorwärts, our party newspaper, and also a Reichstag member. He was historically part of the Majority BBWR that supported our participation in the Great War, but also supports cooperation with the KPP to save the Republic.

- @media_
- @faction_support_
- @kpp_cooperation
- @root: Return to main


