@support_left
on-arrival: repairers_dissent -= 6; repairers_strength += 5

Vorwärts prints editorials in support of Left positions.

@support_liberals
on-arrival: liberals_dissent -= 6; liberals_strength += 5

Vorwärts prints editorials in support of centrist positions.

@support_sanacja_left
on-arrival: sanacja_left_dissent -= 6; sanacja_left_strength += 5

Vorwärts prints editorials in support of the policies of the trade unions.

@support_reform
on-arrival: colonels_dissent -= 6; colonels_strength += 5;

Vorwärts prints editorials in support of the reformist policies.

@support_neorev
view-if: sanacja_nationalists
on-arrival: conservatives_dissent -= 6; conservatives_strength += 5

Vorwärts prints editorials in support of conservatives ideas.

